event.title: The FSFE with a booth and talk at the "Kieler Open Source und Linux Tage" in Kiel, Germany

body.p: The FSFE's local group in Kiel will participate at the the 17th "Kieler Open Source und Linux Tage" with a booth and a talk. Along with that, the FSFE Kiel coordinator, Christian Kalkhoff will have a session, where he will talk about the Public Money? Public Code! campaign.
